# TaskFlow API — Project Rules

## Stack
Node.js + TypeScript (strict mode). Express. PostgreSQL via node-postgres.
Jest + Supertest for tests. All code in src/.

## Folder structure
src/routes/      — Express routers only. No business logic.
src/services/    — All business logic. No direct req/res access.
src/middleware/  — Express middleware (validate, errorHandler).
src/db/          — PostgreSQL pool only.
src/types/       — Shared interfaces and DTOs. No classes.
tests/unit/      — Unit tests for services.
tests/integration/ — Supertest integration tests for routes.
